{"tid":2116863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國有國會眾議員擬提出「防止台灣遭侵略法案」","createTime":"2020-07-20T12:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T12:20:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83ea263399a50673e0f2680a02e8b056a97d683b","tid":2116863,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538823-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538823-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=17863542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538823-20200720.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=22611d02\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538823-20200720.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國有國會眾議員表示，將提出「防止台灣遭侵略法案」，以防中國大陸侵犯台灣。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院外交委員會亞太小組共和黨首席議員約霍接受當地傳媒訪問時表示，美國對台灣和中國大陸的政策，長期存有戰略模糊空間，計劃下周提出「防止台灣遭侵略法案」，清楚闡明美方意向。約霍指出，法案將清楚定明，若中國大陸侵犯台灣，將會授權美國總統動用軍力應對，並且設有5年日落條款。<br />\n<br />\n約霍早前亦聯署支持眾議院版本的「台灣防衛法」草案，要求確保美國履行「台灣關係法」義務，維持阻止大陸武力犯台造成「既成事實」的能力。"},{"pid":"e5ea746880771fee38e46067c160942d2933c1cf","tid":2116863,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jDOzNv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDOzNv1.jpg&h=62b7e60e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗片backup<br />\n何君堯見鄉黑(7 21)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/utmdfj8l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Futmdfj8l&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=f4e539d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/utmdfj8l</a><br />\n立場姐姐被元朗白衣人圍毆片段，亦有記者被打至爆鼻。現場並無任何警察。(7 21)<br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/mzd